{"type": "article", "id": 44633, "title": "烤串外卖也可以变得很酷，来看看这个概念餐厅｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-08-29T22:59:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 43626, "name": "Truly"}, {"id": 38387, "name": "Moisés Hernández"}, {"id": 43627, "name": "Sanwal Deen"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 184, "image": "img/article/article_show/2017082919074905R2pOfHQKs7LgVD.jpeg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Born2Be by Endika Gómez de Balugera et al.</h3><p>你有没有想过外卖烤串也可以变得很酷？最近，来自巴塞罗那高等设计工程学院（ELISAVA）的三位设计师联手创作了一个名为 Born2Be 的概念餐厅，专营可以 DIY 的烤串套餐。打开粉色背景的菜单，左侧的食物选项被设计成了烤串的一部分，不仅一目了然也相当有趣。尽管外卖盒上出现了文艺复兴时期的雕塑，在各种图案与明快配色的衬托下，它们并没有给人一种严肃的感觉。作为一个主打年轻消费者的品牌，每个盒子内还会附赠几张搞怪的贴纸。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829191104gZAN4ma2EKRhBTb8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829191103mLOuNgerhGc5bQHy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829191103726zHOuEYB5nydhD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829191104cYPfF0GaCdEJMO2n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829191104x3GfkjZWRb7DNwen.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Orrery Lamp by Bobby Genalo</h3><p>在 18、19 世纪，一种名为 Orrery 的太阳系仪受到了天文学者的追捧。为了精准地表现、预测星球间的运动以及相对位置，这些仪器在当时往往被建造得相当巨大。为了让更多天文爱好者能够更方便地接触到这个神奇的仪器，洛杉矶设计师 Bobby Genalo 打造了以其为原型的灯饰：灯泡代表太阳，支架上一大一小两个圆球象征地球和月亮。尽管这个毫无智能要素的台灯依然需要用户根据<a href=\"http://www.orrerylamp.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">配套网站</a>给出的位置手动调整，这种桌上太阳系的概念还是相当简洁优雅。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/537191705/orrery-lamp-a-minimal-dimmable-solar-system\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，分为台灯和落地灯两款，均为手工打造，售价从 350 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829190901woU5aCjhzn4Yu3D8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668704\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829190902qYBsChLWSu7rT8cP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.811736\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829190902McVHrvY3XGWZ4psj.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.757353\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829190902mzERjB6VMZo7eTDn.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560294\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829190904D8EvuV3NxP2JgofF.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560294\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>ShooAway</h3><p>夏天约上朋友在户外聚餐，最恼人的就是那些被食物香气吸引来的苍蝇了。厌倦了总得靠挥手赶苍蝇的澳大利亚人 Smithy 为此设计了这款不依靠化学成分驱蝇的机器 ShooAway。它看起来像个简易型风扇，依靠两片柔软且带有特制涂层的金属对苍蝇造成视觉干扰，让它们远离食物。由于内置了感应仪，金属片会自动暂停旋转，拿取食物时也不用担心会弄伤手。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.shooaway.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>，售价为 29.90 澳元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829190846GXdFfBMazCRkxuJy.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.543750\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829190846Mal6gXozUTkeVR5w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829190846aRtp2fqb95XUB8xI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Organs vases by Moisés Hernández</h3><p>与其把所有花草都放在一个花器里，为什么不试着展现每一朵花的独特之处呢？最近，墨西哥设计师 <a href=\"http://www.moises-hernandez.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Moisés Hernández</a> 就推出了一套名为 Organo 的花器，每个花器都由几个大小各异的圆柱形玻璃容器组成，看起来有种像是飘浮在半空里的错觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829190833j0mdDxACq5p87NPI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708291908333jLxThpB9R5XdJ4G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662437\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829190834IjS7b4GvgcFd2Xtw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662437\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829190833Gvlb0ac4eBMj8XV3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708291908348aW7qjuQ5doeiErB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662437\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Work by Sanwal Deen</h3><p>将镜头对准职业人士的摄影作品并不少见，但你见过聚焦在手部的照片吗？这个名为 <a href=\"https://sanwaldeen.com/workphotoproject\" rel=\"nofollow\">Work</a> 的创作项目是美国摄影师 <a href=\"https://sanwaldeen.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sanwal Deen</a> 的最新作品，他希望借此探讨世界各地从事不同职业的人们是否拥有某些相似之处。为了不影响被摄者的工作，Deen 会尽可能快地完成设备搭建与拍摄，这在他看来反而是创作过程中最难的部分。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708291908209GOCyXLiaNQJfqjn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017082919082062A0uqlQkFzPcDHW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708291908205r8usbGiwNDmxl9q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708291908209zqM4wiEWFymVHxY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829190820ZnGH2QS85e9jhWFT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Playground by Truly</h3><p>还记得那个<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/37649.html\">像是虚拟空间的篮球场</a>吗？在今年的意大利都灵市建筑节（<a href=\"http://www.architetturaincitta.it/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Architettura in Città</a>）上，由街头艺术家组成的创作团体 <a href=\"http://wearetruly.it/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Truly</a> 受都灵建筑基金会 <a href=\"http://www.fondazioneperlarchitettura.it/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fondazione per l’architettura</a> 的邀请，在一座篮球场上绘制了 3D 图像。站在篮下的特定位置时，篮球场上的 Growth 和 Rhythm 两个单词就会变得立体，像是球员们在运动时自带特效一样。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708291909539QZg0FlJcMfHVsBq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.734719\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829190953MFwhK578GOCn6kUy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829190954TIxAEh9w738SH5pD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751834\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829190953geIC3dARwSvi7tjH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}